# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Fortress Protocol Frontend Environment Configuration
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values
# This file is safe to commit to git (no secrets)

# Core Configuration
NEXT_PUBLIC_PROGRAM_ID=EB6kkg2sW5rnukjRH7Ljhz78gbfc36XZAuiFn5jdefF3
NEXT_PUBLIC_SOLANA_NETWORK=mainnet-beta

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# THREE-TIER RPC STRATEGY — Fortress Protocol Helius Optimization
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# Get your FREE Helius API key: https://dashboard.helius.dev
# 1. Sign up (no card required)
# 2. Create Application
# 3. Copy API key and paste below

# Gatekeeper RPC (The Speed Pipe) — fastest for user transactions
# https://beta.helius-rpc.com/?api-key=YOUR_KEY
NEXT_PUBLIC_RPC_GATEKEEPER=https://beta.helius-rpc.com/?api-key=YOUR_HELIUS_API_KEY

# Standard RPC (The Stable Pipe) — balanced for background work
# https://mainnet.helius-rpc.com/?api-key=YOUR_KEY
NEXT_PUBLIC_RPC_STANDARD=https://mainnet.helius-rpc.com/?api-key=YOUR_HELIUS_API_KEY

# Public RPC (The Free Pipe) — fallback for non-critical reads
# https://api.mainnet-beta.solana.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_RPC_FREE=https://api.mainnet-beta.solana.com

# Optional: Default RPC endpoint (used as fallback)
NEXT_PUBLIC_RPC_URL=https://api.mainnet-beta.solana.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_RPC_ENDPOINT=https://api.mainnet-beta.solana.com
